  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "Given a positive integer N, convert it into the corresponding Excel column title.\n\nRules:\n\n1 → A\n\n2 → B\n\n…\n\n26 → Z\n\n27 → AA\n\n28 → AB\n\n52 → AZ\n\n53 → BA\n\nand so on…\n\nThis behaves like base-26, but with letters A–Z representing 1–26.\n\n| Input | Output |\n| ----- | ------ |\n| 1     | A      |\n| 26    | Z      |\n| 27    | AA     |\n| 28    | AB     |\n| 37    | AK     |\n| 38    | AL     |",
